title: January 25 2018 Sacramento Jordan Peterson Meetup
description:
I'm organizing a meet-up for January 25 in Sacramento CA. Anyone is welcome.

https://www.meetup.com/Sacramento-Jordan-Peterson-Meetup/events/jccxfpyxcbhc/

This is an interest group. There is no plan for JBP to be here in person. Sorry for the confusion.
